.TH __MS1_XIC_BINS_SINGLE 1 2026-6月 "" "export XIC data for a single rawdata file"
.SH NAME
__ms1_xic_bins_single \- __ms1_xic_bins_single(path,
    <i>mzdiff</i> = <span style='color: green;'>0.005</span>,
    <i>outputdir</i> = <span style='color: brown;'><strong>'./'</strong></span>)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fI__ms1_xic_bins_single(path,
    <i>mzdiff</i> = <span style='color: green;'>0.005</span>,
    <i>outputdir</i> = <span style='color: brown;'><strong>'./'</strong></span>)\fR
.SH OPTIONS
.PP
\fBpath\fB \fR\- . a single rawdata file its file path, should be in mzpack file format.
.PP
.PP
\fBmzdiff\fB \fR\- 0.005. the mass tolerance error in delta dalton for extract the
xic values from the ms1 data.
.PP
.PP
\fBoutputdir\fB \fR\- './'. a directory for save the temp file
.PP
.SH VALUE
.PP
this function returns nothing
.PP
.SH FILES
.PP
SMRUCC/R#.declare_function.__ms1_xic_bins_single at ms1_xic_bins.R:line 81
.PP
